Comment: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.12,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Okay! Cut!
Comment: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:27.83,Default,Guy2,0,0,0,,Wow, the staff around Yunosagi are very capable.
Comment: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:32.96,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I hadn't expected you to bring\N such large-scale equipment with you.
Comment: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:37.21,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,The cameraman works in the special effects department,
Comment: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.05,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,so he's actually better at filming stunts like this.
Comment: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.22,Default,Matsu,0,0,0,,All right! Let's film the next scene!
Comment: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.23,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment, Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:51.35,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Come in.
Comment: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.61,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.04,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Take this.
Comment: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:08.95,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Comment: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.55,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Hello?
Comment: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.97,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, Mom? {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:22.97,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Comment: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling homesick, after your recent visit home?
Comment: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.89,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me get straight to the point. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.14,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}You received an offer for a movie to be shot at the inn, didn't you? {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:33.19,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.44,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't accept that offer, did you? {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.48,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you haven't accepted it yet, that's good. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.11,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I've left Enishi in charge of that.
Comment: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.49,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you saying?! {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.41,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm telling you, something is fishy about the whole thing! {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.95,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can call it off right now by just opening your mouth! {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:50.25,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,This time I don't plan on interfering at all.
Comment: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.62,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, Mom! {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.63,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,How do you feel about inheriting this inn?
Comment: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.97,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Actually, no, Enishi will be the one.
Comment: 0,0:04:04.39,0:04:05.39,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:10.22,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enishi will be the one who inherits Kissui Inn, Mom. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:13.02,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I've just said something pretty foolish, haven't I?
Comment: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.02,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}It wasn't foolish. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:17.90,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it is all in the past now. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.48,Default,Satsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.50,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,That's your job, young master.
Comment: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:38.96,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Right.
Comment: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.71,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Th-Then, shall we?
Comment: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.47,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.64,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Comment: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.31,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,We were watching you from up here!
Comment: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was excellent!
Comment: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.44,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,I hear that they're shooting a film here?
Comment: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:58.19,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,What you were doing was very interesting!
Comment: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.40,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we'll still be at your service as usual.
Comment: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.11,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Comment: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how well you've been taking care of us.
Comment: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.41,Default,Old,0,0,0,,Were you the one who\N jumped from the building just then?
Comment: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't me.
Comment: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:14.33,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,My heart nearly stopped!
Comment: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:15.75,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,In that case,
Comment: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you might want to refrain\N from watching what's coming next.
Comment: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:23.88,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Okay, that's a wrap!
Comment: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:24.92,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Umm...
Comment: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.18,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Comment: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.34,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What's this movie supposed to be about, precisely?
Comment: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.81,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The proposal said, "waitresses in their youth."
Comment: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yuina...
Comment: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:37.56,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.10,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I heard...
Comment: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.02,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Comment: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.98,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That all the madam managers in the\N union don't like this upcoming movie.
Comment: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:50.03,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Well, I think everyone gets a little\N uneasy when trying out something new.
Comment: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:52.16,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Even though they're not the ones staging it?
Comment: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.04,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you be jealous if someone\N became successful at doing something new?
Comment: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:02.04,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I mean, people say that,
Comment: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but there aren't exactly many scenes in this\N film where lots of madam managers appear.
Comment: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.38,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh!
Comment: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:10.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,All the madam managers can\N go to a hot spring for a work trip.
Comment: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.97,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,And then they all become zombies.
Comment: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:13.10,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.65,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,A meal for two in the Paulownia Room, please!
Comment: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.82,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.66,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll take this to the Wisteria Room.
Comment: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.78,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,The meal with the red tag has no green onions in it.
Comment: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.53,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.41,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:34.95,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yes?
Comment: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.25,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh, that explains it.
Comment: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.92,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Explains what?
Comment: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:44.59,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,A customer in the Wisteria\N Room kept staring at my face earlier.
Comment: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.26,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,You know...
Comment: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.22,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll be on my way!
Comment: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.76,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Hey! Get back here!
Comment: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.14,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,The next time we're here, we'll be shooting for real.
Comment: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:54.72,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We'll be waiting.
Comment: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.64,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Mr. Isami.
Comment: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.93,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Comment: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.52,Default,Isami,0,0,0,,Expect great things.
Comment: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:09.03,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,I'm turning this on, young master.
Comment: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:09.90,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Do it.
Comment: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.24,Default,Madam,0,0,0,,I hear it is a scam.
Comment: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.41,Default,Madam2,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Comment: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.21,Default,Madam,0,0,0,,I had my suspicions from the start!
Comment: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.04,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,A scam?
Comment: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.67,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,This has got nothing to do with you.
Comment: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.25,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Leave.
Comment: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.39,Default,Madam,0,0,0,,The folks at Kissui Inn have really done it this time.
Comment: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.64,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako! Takako!
Comment: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.60,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You still haven't managed to contact Mr. Isami?!
Comment: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:27.48,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,No, I only received an e-mail from him\N saying that the project had been called off.
Comment: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.15,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'll try calling him again later.
Comment: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.49,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I had my suspicions about this from the start!
Comment: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.61,Default,Enisih,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.36,Default,Enisih,0,0,0,,You're telling me this {\i1}now{\i0}?
Comment: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.28,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Comment: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:41.45,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,"Don't rush the payment and only pay\N them once you've confirmed that it's safe."
Comment: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:45.12,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, but...
Comment: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:49.29,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Anyway, the contract is under your name, Enishi!
Comment: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.67,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,But you're the one who told me\N about this in the first place, Takako!
Comment: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.47,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I know...
Comment: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.97,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I know that...
Comment: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.35,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,What's going to happen to the young master?
Comment: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.93,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I have no idea...
Comment: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.31,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I did hear he paid them a lot of money, though.
Comment: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:08.06,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,It's his fault for listening to that dumb woman.
Comment: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.57,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,Don't say such things.
Comment: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.98,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I get it!
Comment: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.32,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,"Isami Tetsuo."
Comment: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.91,Default,Tohru,100,100,0,,The characters in his name must stand for,\N "Stepping out of the ring and following someone's mistake!"
Comment: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.12,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'll peel the white radish.
Comment: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:35.67,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I knew that Tohru was tactless, but I still think that a good chef can be.
Comment: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.93,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Oops...
Comment: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.16,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Hey...
Comment: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:07.33,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh, did you hear? The movie's been called off.
Comment: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Too bad we didn't get to act in it.
Comment: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.21,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.88,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Comment: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.21,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,What are you going to do now?
Comment: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.13,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Man, I was really excited.
Comment: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that this would be the summer break to remember.
Comment: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.18,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi was also really excited.
Comment: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What a shame.
Comment: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:33.44,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I rushed here because I thought Kissui Inn\N would be in a mess, but I'm glad to be wrong.
Comment: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:35.69,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I'm heading back now.
Comment: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.36,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What? But you only just got here!
Comment: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.95,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Later!
Comment: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.99,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I guess she doesn't know much about it.
Comment: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.01,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Hello?
Comment: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.05,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is just me talking to myself. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.97,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isami Tetsuo. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:03.64,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's run from debt twice in his life before, {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.97,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}and he was laid off by the people in his industry. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:10.52,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure he's used the money to pay off his debts, {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.52,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}so it'll be too difficult to get it back. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.77,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}The actors and the staff who\N mistakenly got involved with him {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.61,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}are probably going to be in trouble for a while. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.20,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry for the sudden call. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:22.28,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Sis—
Comment: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:32.88,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Hello?
Comment: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.88,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't plan on crying over spilled milk, {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:39.46,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I still don't believe that\N what I was trying to do was wrong. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.80,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Comment: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:44.30,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,But just remember that the\N investors are responsible for the result.
Comment: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.39,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.06,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,I know you know.
Comment: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:52.06,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,But you're also responsible\N for the staff and the customers.
Comment: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:54.15,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're strict as usual. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:59.48,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, everyone makes mistakes.
Comment: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:03.16,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks for the info, Sis. {\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:07.70,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Comment: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.88,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Strawberry flavor is the best after all.
Comment: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.14,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Ohana?
Comment: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.94,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I figured I'd clean the area surrounding the pool.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.85,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,But the movie's been called off.
Comment: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.40,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I've been cleaning the pool every day recently,
Comment: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's sort of become one of my tasks now.
Comment: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.36,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I just can't stand not cleaning it.
Comment: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.99,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Then I'll help you.
Comment: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.95,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Oh, you two are going as well?
Comment: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:48.99,Default,Both,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.95,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Minko's already gone ahead of you.
Comment: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But why?
Comment: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:57.21,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,For the same reason as you.
Comment: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.71,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,That pool isn't only for the movie.
Comment: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:03.92,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Comment: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.72,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Comment: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:09.14,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako!
Comment: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.89,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako, wait!
Comment: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.22,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako!
Comment: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.35,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'm going to Tokyo.
Comment: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a lot of things which I need to take care of.
Comment: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.73,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yes, I know. I want to go with you.
Comment: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.73,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I don't have time to babysit you any longer!
Comment: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.32,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,"Babysit"?
Comment: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.49,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I thought we were partners...
Comment: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.74,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Partners?
Comment: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:31.91,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,You're the one who's responsible for this incident.
Comment: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.75,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'm just an adviser.
Comment: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.58,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,An adviser. Do you understand?!
Comment: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:40.09,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,But, Takako, we handed him the contract together!
Comment: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:44.26,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We discussed it and decided together!
Comment: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.76,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. That—
Comment: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:47.88,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Why don't you...
Comment: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.89,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Why... Why...
Comment: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:55.35,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Why don't you go and ask\N your beloved sister for help then?
Comment: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.60,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Don't you dare say bad things about my sister!
Comment: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.40,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,You're exactly like Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:01.86,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.61,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Sorry, it was a reflex.
Comment: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.32,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Th—
Comment: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.45,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Th-Th—
Comment: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.16,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,That's right!
Comment: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.04,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You're a woman who's able to strike back!
Comment: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.04,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Talking about who's responsible here won't help us at all!
Comment: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:23.59,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I want you to show me how cool you are!
Comment: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.84,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The Takako I always see!
Comment: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.47,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,"We strike back."
Comment: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.47,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,"I shall"—
Comment: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.09,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,No...
Comment: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:32.10,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,"We shall return!"
Comment: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:37.02,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you spouting now?
Comment: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.23,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Just because it's English doesn't\N mean you can just say anything.
Comment: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.15,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,She's right about that.
Comment: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:44.57,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I said, don't mind me!
Comment: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.11,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Wait, Takako!
Comment: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.21,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako!
Comment: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:06.59,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takako, just one more time—
Comment: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.55,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Ta-Takako—
Comment: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.47,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Hey...
Comment: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.40,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Comment: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.41,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Help... me...
Comment: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.53,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Do you want me to hold on or let go?!
Comment: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.41,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Which is it?!
Comment: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:39.25,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Umm... umm...
Comment: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.79,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I can't decide...
Comment: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:45.09,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I can't do this anymore!
Comment: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:47.05,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'm at my limit!
Comment: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.84,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Max limit!
Comment: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.51,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I can't stand this any longer!
Comment: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.68,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, young master?!
Comment: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.05,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I'm also a professional!
Comment: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.26,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,It isn't over yet!
Comment: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.01,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I won't let this be over yet, do you hear?!
Comment: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.90,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Why don't you try standing?
Comment: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:09.48,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,For God's sake...
Comment: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.03,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Here.
Comment: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.37,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What is your {\i1}problem{\i0}?!
Comment: 0,0:16:20.37,0:16:22.37,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,This is my battle gear!
Comment: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.92,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What? Battle gear?
Comment: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:26.38,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Yes! And you're paying for it!
Comment: 0,0:16:26.67,0:16:27.84,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Look what you've done!
Comment: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.00,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,They were expensive!
Comment: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.76,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,So you were wearing your battle gear...
Comment: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:32.42,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.09,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Like I said, they were expensive!
Comment: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.39,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,So, you were serious, Takako?
Comment: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:38.72,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.10,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.02,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thank you, Takako.
Comment: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:45.19,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You're not at fault. You tried your best!
Comment: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.98,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What the heck are you saying?!
Comment: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.27,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,I've always said that your independent and
Comment: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,peculiar way of thinking is one of your major flaws—
Comment: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.28,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:55.11,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thanks, and don't worry.
Comment: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:56.99,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Let's start again together.
Comment: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.28,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Let go of me.
Comment: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.12,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,This time, we'll do it together.
Comment: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.59,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Only thinking about themselves.
Comment: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.18,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Comment: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:21.14,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.31,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We shouldn't watch any more.
Comment: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.78,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You can keep going.
Comment: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:39.74,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,But your clothes...
Comment: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.33,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Comment: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.79,Default,Bean,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Comment: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:48.63,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I thought I'd act like a mother for once.
Comment: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:57.05,Default,Madam,0,0,0,,Kissui Inn's got a lot to take care of now.
Comment: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:01.64,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Well, I hate to say this, but\N they brought this upon themselves.
Comment: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:04.31,Default,woman,0,0,0,,They were walking on air, weren't they?
Comment: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:06.39,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Hey, it felt good.
Comment: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:10.90,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I did walk on air when I leaped from the second story window.
Comment: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.28,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Bang! Bang! Bang!
Comment: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:16.61,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,There was also a scene like that.
Comment: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:19.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Comment: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.95,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear the bad news.
Comment: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:31.04,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I thought it would be best if I let\N you, the representatives of Yunosagi,
Comment: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:36.55,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,know of our current situation.
Comment: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:39.84,Default,Renji,0,0,0,,The meal for the Wave Room is ready.
Comment: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.76,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Is the sashimi for the Crane Room still not ready?
Comment: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.93,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Nope, it is!
Comment: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'll be taking this.
Comment: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.15,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.69,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,What's with that outfit?
Comment: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:58.70,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Well...
Comment: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.11,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Come to my room.
Comment: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:01.95,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.41,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,How's everyone doing?
Comment: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.95,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,They're all doing well.
Comment: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.00,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Madam Manager,
Comment: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.38,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I should've been the one to go and explain.
Comment: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.59,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, and I apologize.
Comment: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.55,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,But Ms. Kawajiri really had Kissui Inn on her mind,
Comment: 0,0:19:21.55,0:19:24.55,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,and did her best to make things work.
Comment: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.26,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,No matter what you say,
Comment: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kawajiri will have to take\N her share of the responsibility.
Comment: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.77,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Be prepared for that.
Comment: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.61,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.27,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You can call me "Mom".
Comment: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.48,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Oh... okay.
Comment: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:41.15,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom, I'm not defending her or anything.
Comment: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.61,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,She really was trying her best.
Comment: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.58,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You can tell me this later.
Comment: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.96,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,More importantly,
Comment: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you've grown enough\N to be able to defend someone so much.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.75,0:20:03.34,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I never understood whether you\N were simply stubborn or just clumsy.
Comment: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.26,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the piano lessons?
Comment: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.06,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,During high school,
Comment: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously thought that being able to\N play an instrument would get me the girls.
Comment: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:20.28,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,But you kept refusing to take lessons in elementary school.
Comment: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:24.82,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,If only you'd put a collar on\N me and taken me to those lessons,
Comment: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:28.33,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,my teenage life would have been a lot different.
Comment: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.21,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You were a terrible swimmer too.
Comment: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:37.09,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I still am, Mom.
Comment: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.13,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Comment: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:22.13,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom...
Comment: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:25.51,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Mom!
Comment: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.15,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Ohana!
Comment: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:46.95,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Look! It's done!
Comment: 4,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.29,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,What a funny looking cloud...
Comment: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:35.05,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,If I were a mermaid princess...
Comment: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:38.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I wouldn't admire a prince...
Comment: 1,0:23:38.43,0:23:41.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,because... land is scary.
